name: 07 Memory Card - Lugano
description: Born in Switzerland to Korean parents who work at the embassy. Lugano grew up and lived with his grandmother in the Sarasvati district. He grew up to be an independent and quiet introverted person. He finally decided to become a "White Hat Hacker" in one of the biggest companies in Lucid City. He only has a few close friends, including Mon, who often takes him around the alleys exploring culinary delights and listening to their favorite songs together on weekends.
